						               													<description>Two cosmic adventurers are in a tricky scenario and must work together. By rolling and manipulating dice for special abilities and combos, you can be the one that guides them to victory.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Liberation Forces are decimated, paving the way for control of the galaxy's Inner Ring. &amp;ldquo;But you promised me a real fight.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Suddenly, the comm crackles to life, &amp;quot;Commander! Liberation reinforcements are dropping out of hyperspace!&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;Ah, your playmates have arrived... Now off with you, I'll bring the weapon online.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;An all new Twin Stars scenario! In this one, we see a doctor and patient both trying to survive to win. It comes with two new character cards (Fanooba and Inpon Gol) which can be combined / exchanged with other sets.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Stop the Virus, help a doctor through the care of a fading patient. Control the viruses, stamina &amp;amp; health to survive. You must heal the patient, then survive three days of quarantine to win. If either of you run out of health, you lose.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Stop the Virus is a scenario in the Twin Stars solo system by Jason Tagmire and Mike Mullins. The game consists of just 3 cards and players will provide their own dice and coins/tokens. Each scenario comes with 2 all-new characters and can be interchanged with others for a very different gaming experience.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game was originally offered as a stretch goal for Button Shy's Universal Rule Kickstarter.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
